On Motion of the State, the Court amends the single charge in the Case #14CF397 Information to three counts of Class A Misdemeanor Retail Theft as set forth in the "Criminal Case Settlement" form. 

Constitutional rights reviewed; pleas of "Guilty" entered on Counts #1, #2, #3 in Case #14CF397, all contrary to Statute 943.50(1m)(b) and (4)(a); factual basis stipulated; the Court accepts the pleas, finds Ms. Shamble guilty, and orders Judgment of Conviction entered.

On agreement of the parties, the Court reads-in and dismisses Case #14CM449.

On Case #14CF397 Count #1:
--the Court sentences Ms. Shamble to serve two months in Jail, with Huber privileges, consecutive to Dodge County Case #14CM158 or any other sentence in being.
